dataIdInfo.idPurp: This data was compiled for Cross Cultural Consulting Services (CCCS) to complete their social study in Maluku, Indonesia.
dataIdInfo.idAbs: Airport data at Scale 1:250,000. Data was taken from Ministry of Transportation Republic Indonesia, accessed through their ArcGIS Service (http://gis.dephub.go.id/arcgis/rest/services). Update unknown.
